  "text": "Secondly, although Vri and Pdp1ε ε are both activated by Clk-Cyc, Pdp1ε ε mRNA accumulation is delayed compared to that of Vri [CITATION_1] . This delay produces a concomitant delay in PDP1ε ε accumulation, which counteracts Vri dependent repression and consequently activates Clk and Cry. Understanding the mechanism that governs Pdp1ε ε mRNA accumulation will be important for understanding how rhythmic transcription within and downstream of the Clk loop is controlled.",
